OL,3,CMan appears in court to deny murder of
OL,4,CUniversity of Lancashire student
OL,6,FA man has denied murdering a
OL,7,Funiversity student found dead in her
OL,8,Fhalls of residence in Preston.
OL,10,FCarla Georgescu's body was discovered
OL,11,Fin University of Lancashire student
OL,12,Faccommodation in Victoria Street,
OL,13,FPreston, on Thursday 5 February.
OL,15,FNathan Owens, 34, of Hopps Street,
OL,16,FHartlepool, Durham, has been charged
OL,17,Fwith the second-year student's murder.
OL,19,FOwens has also been charged with
OL,20,Fintentional strangulation and Section
OL,21,F18 grievous bodily harm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
