OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776146706
OL,3,CMan appears in court to deny murder of
OL,4,CUniversity of Lancashire student
OL,6,FHe appeared at Preston Crown Court on
OL,7,FMonday 13 April and denied murdering
OL,8,Fher.
OL,10,FCarla, who was born in Bucharest,
OL,11,FRomania, was a second year student at
OL,12,FUCLan when she died.
OL,14,FAn inquest into her death was opened
OL,15,Fand adjourned to allow criminal
OL,16,Fproceedings to take place.
OL,18,FFollowing her death, a candlelit vigil
OL,19,Fwas held at the university in memory
OL,20,Fof the second year clinical psychology
OL,21,Fstudent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
