CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776146706
OL,3,CMan appears in court to deny murder of
OL,4,CUniversity of Lancashire student
OL,6,FCarla was described by her personal
OL,7,Ftutor and course leader as a "warm,
OL,8,Fbright, engaging and enthusiastic"
OL,9,Fstudent.
OL,11,FHe said she was "working hard every
OL,12,Fday to realise her dream of becoming a
OL,13,Fclinical practitioner."
OL,15,F"Her kindness and her readiness to
OL,16,Fengage were gifts she brought not only
OL,17,Fto her studies but to everyone around
OL,18,Fher and tonight we hold those memories
OL,19,Fclose,"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
